  "body": "- it would be better if remixd isn't dependant on `npm`, (be installed with `npm install remixd`) but can be installed as a standalone app (having a UI or not).\r\n \r\n - we should introduce a simple and clear UI (do we still keep CLI? - yes)\r\n \r\n - if remixd UI serves remix IDE, we could imagine deprecating remix desktop and keep remixd UI + a served remix IDE (that is subject to discussion)\r\n\r\n- do we need a logo for remixd? I would suggest having at least a Remi (plugins to connect together?)\r\n",
